title: Winn-Dixie Jacksonville Open
text:
The Winn-Dixie Jacksonville Open was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Web.com%20Tour">Web.com Tour</a> from 2010 to 2012. It was played for the first time in October 2010 at <a href="TPC%20Sawgrass">TPC Sawgrass</a>'s Dye's Valley Course in <a href="Ponte%20Vedra%20Beach%2C%20Florida">Ponte Vedra Beach, Florida</a>. The 2012 purse was <a href="United%20States%20dollar">US$</a>600,000, with $108,000 going to the winner.

Bolded golfers graduated to the PGA Tour via the final Web.com Tour money list.
